snippet.title: CG Cookie
snippet.description:
Learning Blender 3d? We got you. ❤️

CG Cookie is a small crew of 3d artists making amazing Blender training - for you. Check back often for Blender beginner training tips, tutorials, course trailers, and live streams. 

Subscribe to this channel to stay on top of Blender. If you love what we do and are craving to seriously learn Blender, become a member at CG Cookie - http://cgcookie.com 

Happy Blending!
